professor to Harvard

00:00:53.636 --> 00:00:55.260
from the American
University of Beirut.

00:00:55.260 --> 00:00:57.629
And then Harvard said,
stay another year stay,

00:00:57.629 --> 00:00:58.170
another year.

00:00:58.170 --> 00:01:00.600
He never went back.

