00:46:51.100 --> 00:46:52.250
away from my face.

00:46:52.250 --> 00:46:52.750
OK.

00:46:52.750 --> 00:46:54.190
You saw that, right?

00:46:54.190 --> 00:46:58.420
So you tell me now,
you tell me what

00:46:58.420 --> 00:47:00.100
happens when I close the book?

00:47:00.100 --> 00:47:01.900
What happened when
